entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="あいつら、あたしたちを何だと思ってるの？ ここがコーポ・プラザにでも見える？" t="Who do they think we are? Does this look like Corpo Plaza to you?" b="" a=""/>
Try as I might, can't imagine that. Not even fucking close.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="じゃあなんでこんな堅苦しい生活をしなきゃいけないの！" t="So why do I feel like I live in goddamned Corpo Plaza?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="なにが“警備”料金よ？ クロウズの奴ら、今年に入ってもう3回も値上げしやがって！" t="Think our \"security\" fees could have something to do with it? Tygers asked for more! Again! Third time this year!" b="" a=""/>
Hey, hey, not so loud. Walls have ears, you don't want trouble.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="あたしには小さな子供が2人と、BDアクターを目指す夫がいるの。タイガークロウズでもなんでも、かかってきなさいよ" t="I have two small kids and an aspiring BD actor for a husband. The Tyger Claws are my entertainment." b="" a=""/>
I getcha. Still, wouldn't want those kids to lose their mother, would ya?
